itzcoatl ( , " obsidian serpent " ) was the fourth king of the aztecs of tenochtitlan and the first emperor , ruling from 1427 ( or 1428 ) to 1440 , the period when the mexicathe dominant ethno - political group within the later aztec political sphere . threw off the domination of the tepanecs and laid the foundations for the eventual aztec empire .

